message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which holds immense value and potential for growth. I understand its worth to you stands at $800,000, and I believe we can bridge the gap to ensure both parties benefit. My offer to you is $950,000 for the product. This price reflects not only its current value but also the future opportunities it can provide. I look forward to discussing this further and exploring how we can make this transaction beneficial for both of us.
